OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FVatican court convicts     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fformer Pope adviser of     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffinancial crimes           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Vatican court has sentenced Italian  
OL,6, Cardinal Angelo Becciu, a former       
OL,7, adviser to Pope Francis, to            
OL,8, five-and-a-half years in jail for      
OL,9, financial crimes.                      
OL,11,FBecciu, 75, was the most senior Vatican
OL,12,Fofficial ever to face such charges and 
OL,13,Fonce seen as a papal contender himself.
OL,15,FThe trial centred on a London property 
OL,16,Fdeal that ended in huge losses for the 
OL,17,FCatholic Church.                       
OL,19,FHe strongly denied charges including   
OL,20,Fembezzlement and abuse of office.      
